Cyrinda Foxe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyrinda_Foxe 0 Cyrinda Foxe (born Kathleen Victoria Hetzekian; February 22, 1952 – September 7, 2002) was an American actress, model and publicist, best known for her role in Andy Warhol's Bad (1977). She was married to both David Johansen of the proto-punk band New York Dolls and Steven Tyler of the hard rock band Aerosmith. She was the mother of Mia Tyler.
